<section id="section-6">
<title> Two blocks system  </title>

<para id="element-71">
<term> Problem 5 : </term> Two blocks "A" and "B", weighing 20 N and 10 N respectively are in contact with each other. If the blocks are at rest, then find the force "F" and the normal reactions between all contact surfaces.
</para>
<para id="element-72">
<figure id="fig-72">
<title> Balanced force system </title>
<media id="id15852429" alt=""><image src="../../media/bfs12.gif" mime-type="image/gif"/></media>
</figure>
</para>
<para id="element-73">
